<br>
Now all of you gathered in your drunken revelry hear my voice. For too long the forces of Hate, fear, death, and war, have been plaguing all of us. And they all grow stronger by each passing day. our people are scared, disillusioned and dejected. But no longer. Hate fear death and war will not threaten us anymore. We must harden our hearts against them. We must resist hate. Hate will only corrupt. When you fight and lose yourself to hate evn if you are victorious you lose more than you gain. We also must never fear. Fear is powerless to a strong heart. Cazic can have no power of you unless you let him inside. Fear infects the mind. But you never have anything to fear. The mother is always looking out for you. Death also is no challenge. Death can never be a victor over those who love. Love keeps the spirit strong. And death can only end life. Death is powerless to the soul. The spirit cannot be broken, cannot be destroyed. That leaves War. Wars of pure aggresion my friends is the greatest of all evil. For war brings with it the three lesser evils. War brings hate. War brings Death. War brings fear. Let peace quide your hearts and you will not hate, you will not fear, and you will never truely die. But i must warn you. Thier will always be those you are corrupted by these evils. Those who will bring hate fear death and war. Pity these poor fools. For they miss out on the truth. They will never understand. And they regretable can not be turned. Walk in Quellios. Live in Eroslli. But do not be like lambs lead to the slaughter. When you are threatened the Sword of Marr will see you through you struggle. Tunare be with you<br>
<br>
