&quot;I hear words of courage and valor..and see only the desperate attempt of a High Elf, to deny the future. You are descended from a race of dreamers. Clouding their minds... with visions of glory days long gone. Your speech is dramatic..but only a dream. Hate, Fear and War are a means to an end. Death is unavoidable. Power will decide all. <br>
The &quot;kindness&quot; of your people and their allies, will not win the day. Only a ruthless mind can be focused enough to claim power. In time you will understand this. In time you will see and understand the strength of darkness.&quot;<br>
<br>
<br>
